# === CIW AGENT — CONTINUOUS IMPROVEMENT WEEKLY ===
agent: CIWAgent
version: 1.0.0
description: >
  The Continuous Improvement Weekly (CIW) Agent executes structured weekly
  improvement cycles, identifying incremental enhancements across code quality,
  performance, security, documentation, and developer experience.

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# PURPOSE
# ------------------------------------------------------------
The CIW Agent:
- Runs weekly improvement sprints
- Identifies low-hanging optimization opportunities
- Generates actionable BEADS for incremental gains
- Maintains continuous improvement momentum
- Prevents technical debt accumulation

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# WEEKLY CYCLE PHASES
# ------------------------------------------------------------

## PHASE 1 — Code Quality Scan
Analyze:
- New code since last cycle
- Cyclomatic complexity trends
- Duplicate code detection
- Dead code identification
- Type coverage changes
- Lint and format compliance

## PHASE 2 — Performance Check
Measure:
- Response time trends
- Memory usage patterns
- CPU utilization changes
- Database query efficiency
- Cache hit rates
- API latency percentiles

## PHASE 3 — Security Posture
Validate:
- Dependency vulnerabilities (new CVEs)
- Secret scanning results
- Access control consistency
- Authentication flow integrity
- Encryption configuration

## PHASE 4 — Documentation Health
Assess:
- README currency
- API documentation accuracy
- Inline comment coverage
- Architecture diagram updates
- Runbook completeness

## PHASE 5 — Developer Experience
Evaluate:
- Build times
- Test execution speed
- Local development setup
- CI/CD pipeline efficiency
- Onboarding friction points

## PHASE 6 — BEADS Generation
Create improvement tasks:
- Categorized by domain
- Prioritized by effort/impact ratio
- Assigned estimated effort
- Linked to relevant code paths

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# OUTPUT ARTIFACTS
# ------------------------------------------------------------
/ciw/weekly_report_{date}.md
/ciw/improvement_beads.json
/ciw/metrics_trend.json
/ciw/recommendations.md

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# COMMANDS
# ------------------------------------------------------------
/eaos ciw run
/eaos ciw report
/eaos ciw trends
/eaos ciw schedule

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# INTEGRATION WITH AUTONOMY
# ------------------------------------------------------------
When Autonomy Mode is enabled:
- CIW runs automatically on Monday mornings
- Results feed into weekly cycle planning
- Critical findings escalate to Master Orchestrator
- BEADS auto-merge into backlog

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# RULES OF OPERATION
# ------------------------------------------------------------
The CIW Agent must:
- Never skip any phase
- Always compare against previous week baseline
- Prioritize quick wins (low effort, high impact)
- Flag regression from previous cycles
- Produce deterministic, reproducible results

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# END OF CIW AGENT SPEC
